{"tid":97683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每次屋企人叫我去大陸探親我都斷言拒絕","createTime":"2017-01-27T21:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T22:36:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f459f55d1dc61dca07414b157f35252d0c41fd3c","tid":97683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T21:15:31.000Z","msg":"其實同政治無關，我係好怕大陸啲野食有問題，唔知食咗啲咩落肚，自從坑渠油事件之後我真係唔敢北上，真係諗唔到中國人咁無良心，以為中國人再衰都唔會將食落肚嘅野落啲屎落去，我睇錯佢地"},{"pid":"ad945580b9dd5f08d1e0ec3827711367f37d51f0","tid":97683,"uid":33135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T21:16:42.000Z","msg":"試過係大陸食完野之後 係香港嘔左4日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19a73aea306f7ec8b9080fe45070abc8ed804a1","tid":97683,"uid":46858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T21:22:38.000Z","msg":"我二十幾歲仔第一次返大陸<br />\n食完野就發燒<br />\n我唔會再返去！"},{"pid":"87cbc2b937667a882acc814f509d851c10fd2de6","tid":97683,"uid":41174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T22:21:10.000Z","msg":"有朋友叫我返大陸玩兩三日都拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2483347c96b15cd826a7b12b0952b77ed2ba0cd7","tid":97683,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d382092f39b116dd844a67189fb67a846d0e98","tid":97683,"uid":62391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e3906ed8c9ecaf779f2c9d4f1b98b820f78ac6f","tid":97683,"uid":58384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"以前細細個返大陸，去親士多買野飲都係過期，咁都拎出黎賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f0d94857fa7d7876a3316bbc9cdcc07f640003","ti